from Longwan Company,

81
00:03:43,100 --> 00:03:44,630
are mostly vague.

82
00:03:45,380 --> 00:03:47,360
They all claim

83
00:03:47,840 --> 00:03:49,030
it was a violent clash

84
00:03:49,030 --> 00:03:50,240
triggered by a business dispute

85
00:03:50,240 --> 00:03:51,430
between He Biao and Liu Tianye.

86
00:03:51,430 --> 00:03:53,150
According to Ding Xiaoshuai's
statement afterward,

87
00:03:53,150 --> 00:03:55,030
after the talks between
He Biao and Liu Tianye

88
00:03:55,030 --> 00:03:56,060
broke down,

89
00:03:56,240 --> 00:03:57,360
He Biao waited for a chance to retaliate

90
00:03:57,360 --> 00:03:58,730
and abducted him.

91
00:03:59,030 --> 00:04:00,030
In a state of panic, Ding Xiaoshuai

92
00:04:00,030 --> 00:04:01,600
was involved in

93
00:04:01,800 --> 00:04:03,060
a car accident.

94
00:04:03,310 --> 00:04:04,680
All the accomplices insist

95
00:04:04,680 --> 00:04:07,120
that Liu Tianye, Liu Tianfei,
and the others

96
00:04:07,120 --> 00:04:08,960
had no knowledge of the incident.

97
00:04:08,960 --> 00:04:10,320
At present, there is no direct evidence

98
00:04:10,320 --> 00:04:13,340
linking Liu Tianye, Liu Tianfei,
or the others to the case.

99
00:04:13,340 --> 00:04:16,339
We will continue with
a more in-depth investigation.

100
00:04:17,430 --> 00:04:18,690
What else did you find?

101
00:04:19,120 --> 00:04:20,649
We discovered three bodies

102
00:04:21,240 --> 00:04:22,430
on a fishing boat.

103
00:04:23,310 --> 00:04:25,240
The perpetrator is still unknown.

104
00:04:25,480 --> 00:04:27,670
On He Biao's yacht,

105
00:04:28,000 --> 00:04:29,040
we found

106
00:04:29,160 --> 00:04:29,870
gambling equipment,

107
00:04:29,870 --> 00:04:30,630
IOUs,

108
00:04:30,630 --> 00:04:31,270
and

109
00:04:31,560 --> 00:04:32,820
a large amount of cash.

110
00:04:33,560 --> 00:04:35,090
Based on the earlier leads,

111
00:04:35,310 --> 00:04:36,830
we can basically determine

112
00:04:36,830 --> 00:04:38,090
that He Biao and He Gang

113
00:04:38,510 --> 00:04:40,510
are suspected of
organizing illegal gambling,

114
00:04:40,510 --> 00:04:41,440
loan-sharking,

115
00:04:41,510 --> 00:04:42,159
and

116
00:04:42,480 --> 00:04:44,480
violent debt collection.

117
00:04:45,159 --> 00:04:47,090
What about the person who killed He Gang?

118
00:04:47,090 --> 00:04:47,390
[Hanzhou Public Security]

119
00:04:47,390 --> 00:04:48,450
He is very elusive.

120
00:04:49,120 --> 00:04:50,230
We interviewed

121
00:04:50,480 --> 00:04:52,140
drivers at the logistics hub,

122
00:04:52,560 --> 00:04:53,690
but no one knows

123
00:04:54,560 --> 00:04:55,830
his real name

124
00:04:55,920 --> 00:04:56,720
or address.

125
00:04:57,190 --> 00:04:58,270
All they know is

126
00:04:58,720 --> 00:05:00,250
that he lives in his vehicle

127
00:05:00,600 --> 00:05:02,530
and likes eating sunflower seeds,

128
00:05:02,630 --> 00:05:04,720
so everyone calls him "Guazi."

129
00:05:06,240 --> 00:05:08,680
Based on the biological evidence
left at the scene,

130
00:05:08,680 --> 00:05:09,750
we can confirm

131
00:05:10,040 --> 00:05:11,560
that he has no prior criminal record.

132
00:05:11,560 --> 00:05:14,490
According to information
provided by Mai Hongchao,

133
00:05:15,040 --> 00:05:16,340
Su Hongbao's death

134
00:05:16,510 --> 00:05:18,310
is very likely connected to him.

135
00:05:18,310 --> 00:05:19,360
It's even possible

136
00:05:19,360 --> 00:05:21,000
that he was involved in

137
00:05:22,040 --> 00:05:23,640
the Xu Li case from years ago.

138
00:05:23,830 --> 00:05:25,070
For someone

139
00:05:25,070 --> 00:05:27,120
to stay hidden under our noses

140
00:05:27,750 --> 00:05:29,270
for so many years

141
00:05:31,310 --> 00:05:33,159
means he has someone backing him.

142
00:05:33,159 --> 00:05:34,159
He's not simple.

143
00:05:35,480 --> 00:05:37,000
Contact the provincial department
immediately

144
00:05:37,000 --> 00:05:37,930
and issue an APB.

145
00:05:38,240 --> 00:05:38,950
Yes.

146
00:05:44,950 --> 00:05:46,360
