168
00:06:37,600 --> 00:06:38,560
The key issue is

169
00:06:38,800 --> 00:06:40,120
that both He Biao and He Gang

170
00:06:40,120 --> 00:06:41,000
are dead,

171
00:06:41,510 --> 00:06:43,440
and there's no concrete evidence.

172
00:06:44,480 --> 00:06:45,280
Investigate.

173
00:06:48,510 --> 00:06:49,560
I suggest

174
00:06:50,120 --> 00:06:50,980
