700
00:32:41,440 --> 00:32:42,830
I noticed it when I came in.

701
00:32:42,830 --> 00:32:44,230
It looks much softer now,

702
00:32:44,350 --> 00:32:45,670
not like your style.

703
00:32:45,920 --> 00:32:46,960
My son likes it.

704
00:32:47,300 --> 00:32:48,950
Well, Mr. Liu,

705
00:32:49,590 --> 00:32:50,820
I heard that you

706
00:32:51,000 --> 00:32:53,600
had a little misunderstanding
with Ms. Zhang.

707
00:32:54,050 --> 00:32:56,980
Since we're meeting today,
shall we talk it through?

708
00:32:58,070 --> 00:32:58,950
This gravel business

709
00:32:58,950 --> 00:32:59,070
[Zhao Peng,
General Manager of Pengfei Construction]

710
00:32:59,070 --> 00:33:00,750
has always been ours.

711
00:33:01,790 --> 00:33:02,720
Recently,

712
00:33:02,790 --> 00:33:05,120
I don't know
where Mr. Zhou popped up from—

713
00:33:06,030 --> 00:33:07,200
he's trying to grab our mine

714
00:33:07,200 --> 00:33:08,660
and even hurt a few people.

715
00:33:10,860 --> 00:33:12,240
Mr. Zhou is my friend.

716
00:33:12,550 --> 00:33:14,750
He used to be in the gravel business too.

717
00:33:14,830 --> 00:33:16,300
He thinks your mine is good

718
00:33:16,400 --> 00:33:17,160
and wants it.

719
00:33:19,680 --> 00:33:21,210
Then let him come alone.

720
00:33:21,270 --> 00:33:22,870
I'll wait for him at the mine.

721
00:33:22,960 --> 00:33:24,560
No need to be sneaky about it.

722
00:33:24,960 --> 00:33:25,890
We already

723
00:33:26,070 --> 00:33:27,270
agreed on this.

724
00:33:32,450 --> 00:33:34,850
That's business, right? Everyone does it.

725
00:33:34,960 --> 00:33:35,560
Ms. Zhang,

726
00:33:35,920 --> 00:33:37,250
if your friend likes it,

727
00:33:37,270 --> 00:33:37,750
take it.

728
00:33:39,960 --> 00:33:41,290
That's how it should be.

729
00:33:41,640 --> 00:33:42,840
What's yours and mine

730
00:33:43,070 --> 00:33:44,160
is ours.

731
00:33:44,310 --> 00:33:45,840
Let's make money together.

732
00:33:47,240 --> 00:33:48,100
Director Chen,

733
00:33:48,270 --> 00:33:49,920
I got a few bottles of top-notch red wine.

734
00:33:49,920 --> 00:33:50,920
Let's enjoy it shortly.

735
00:33:50,920 --> 00:33:51,520
Everyone,

736
00:33:51,790 --> 00:33:52,850
the lunch is ready.

737
00:33:53,030 --> 00:33:53,880
Please come this way.

738
00:33:53,880 --> 00:33:54,410
Let's go.

739
00:33:55,310 --> 00:33:56,270
I'll skip the meal.

740
00:33:56,270 --> 00:33:57,590
I've got plans to go horseback riding
with your sister.

741
00:33:57,590 --> 00:33:58,790
-Today? Horseback riding?
-Yeah.

742
00:33:58,790 --> 00:33:59,550
Why not eat first, then ride?

743
00:33:59,550 --> 00:34:00,440
Ask her to join us.

744
00:34:00,440 --> 00:34:01,550
No, no, next time.

745
00:34:01,590 --> 00:34:02,720
I have a meeting this afternoon

746
00:34:02,720 --> 00:34:03,680
and I might be late.

747
00:34:03,680 --> 00:34:04,640
I'll pass on lunch too.

748
00:34:04,640 --> 00:34:06,590
You two planned this together, didn't you?

749
00:34:06,590 --> 00:34:07,400
Are you really not eating?

750
00:34:07,400 --> 00:34:08,110
No, thanks.

751
00:34:08,110 --> 00:34:08,840
Let me see you off.

752
00:34:08,840 --> 00:34:09,620
No need, please stay.

753
00:34:09,620 --> 00:34:10,650
Come on, let me see you out.

754
00:34:10,650 --> 00:34:12,000
-Sisi, bring two gift boxes.
-You're welcome.

755
00:34:12,000 --> 00:34:12,590
Okay.

756
00:34:13,840 --> 00:34:15,360
Skipping the meal
and going horseback riding.

757
00:34:15,360 --> 00:34:16,960
Will you have enough energy?

758
00:34:26,000 --> 00:34:26,710
Xin.

759
00:34:27,000 --> 00:34:28,360
Jiangyan, you're here.

760
00:34:29,550 --> 00:34:30,480
Sorry

761
00:34:30,710 --> 00:34:31,840
to keep you waiting.

762
00:34:32,070 --> 00:34:33,670
I just came back from
your brother's place.

763
00:34:33,670 --> 00:34:34,800
We had a little chat.

764
00:34:35,320 --> 00:34:36,380
I just arrived too.

765
00:34:36,790 --> 00:34:38,850
How's my brother's business lately?

766
00:34:38,880 --> 00:34:40,710
He's your brother. Why ask me?

767
00:34:42,670 --> 00:34:44,600
I'll change clothes. Let's begin.

768
00:34:44,630 --> 00:34:45,190
Let's go.

769
00:34:45,550 --> 00:34:46,110
Meng Yu,

770
00:34:46,230 --> 00:34:47,190
help Ms. Wen with his bag.
Sure.

771
00:34:47,190 --> 00:34:47,630
Okay.

772
00:34:50,070 --> 00:34:51,139
Who's this?

773
00:34:51,360 --> 00:34:52,690
She's my new assistant.

774
00:34:52,760 --> 00:34:54,550
Xinrui has those work-study projects

775
00:34:54,550 --> 00:34:56,000
with a few universities.

776
00:34:56,360 --> 00:34:58,280
She's good with languages,
so she can do translation.

777
00:34:58,280 --> 00:35:00,280
I kept her as my personal secretary.

778
00:35:00,840 --> 00:35:01,560
Meng Yu, say hello to Ms. Wen.

779
00:35:01,560 --> 00:35:02,590
[Meng Yu, Zhang Xin's personal secretary]

780
00:35:02,590 --> 00:35:03,440
Hello, Ms. Wen.

781
00:35:03,440 --> 00:35:04,240
Hello. Hello.

782
00:35:04,280 --> 00:35:06,140
Xin rarely brings someone along—

783
00:35:06,280 --> 00:35:07,740
you should learn from her.

784
00:35:08,440 --> 00:35:09,110
Yes.

785
00:35:10,120 --> 00:35:13,860
[Hangang Center Construction Site]

786
00:35:35,320 --> 00:35:37,190
Keep me company riding a bit longer today.

787
00:35:37,190 --> 00:35:37,920
No problem.

788
00:35:38,480 --> 00:35:39,010
Let's go.

789
00:35:39,110 --> 00:35:39,710
Ms. Zhang,

790
00:35:40,000 --> 00:35:40,630
your call.

791
00:35:41,950 --> 00:35:42,440
Okay.

792
00:35:42,670 --> 00:35:44,000
You all go change your clothes first.

793
00:35:44,000 --> 00:35:44,530
Alright.

794
00:35:52,220 --> 00:35:54,730
[Hanzhou Emergency Center]

795
00:35:54,810 --> 00:35:56,920
[Police]

796
00:35:57,510 --> 00:35:59,190
This afternoon, a collapse occurred

797
00:35:59,190 --> 00:36:00,320
